latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A simple, soft and chewy granola bars recipe which is easy and quick to make.
Made up of rolled and instant oats, some seeds, nuts, olive oil, honey and brown sugar!
Packed with proteins, good fats and delicious taste🤗

I have used parchment paper and paper foil to wrap it from @oddy_uniwraps 

You need
1/2 cup each of instant and rolled oats
Some seeds and nuts
Pinch of salt
3tbsp brown sugar
1/4 cup honey
3tbsp olive oil
some chocolate chips (optional)

Spaghetti salad 🌿

This easy salad is low in calorie, perfect option for weight loss🙌
